parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering assist can cause the steering wheel to become firm or difficult to turn, making it challenging to maneuver the vehicle, especially at low speeds, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering assist fault light comes on
the steering wheel becomes firm or difficult to turn
the vehicle is hard to maneuver
especially at low speeds
the power steering assist message appears on the instrument panel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the turbo boost can cause the vehicle to smoke excessively, leading to a potential fire hazard, and can also cause the engine to stutter or lose power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle smokes excessively
the check engine light comes on
the oil light comes on
the vehicle makes a ding sound
the vehicle stutters or loses power
the vehicle is difficult to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the turbocharger can cause engine damage, oil leaks, and decreased engine performance, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Warning of low oil pressure
engine light on
blown turbos
oil shooting into the engine
emission problems
catalytic converter issues
hard shifting
lack of power
rattling or knocking sound when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The hard shifting and lack of power can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Hard shifting when rolling down or driving in bumper-to-bumper traffic
lack of power
rattling or knocking sound when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the 20" aluminum wheels can lead to tire pressure deflation, which can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Advanced corrosion and deep pitting of the chrome near the wheel mounting studs and between the spokes
corrosion of the wheel flange
tire pressure deflation at an increasing rate
wheel damage despite regular washing and waxing.
